Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zabi family seeks to impose dictatorship\Nover all of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...ruling from the Principality of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...a gigantic space city-state\Nfloating beyond the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Degwin Zabi ceded his power\Nto his eldest son, Gihren Zabi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...and war broke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Faced with the superior preparation\Nof the Zeon forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:02:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Earth Federation Forces\Nwere helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoiding Zeon's attacks and\Nescaping from Side 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base, piloted by\Nits youthful crew, returned to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After bringing down Garma Zabi,\Nthe youngest member of the Zabi family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...it is currently crossing the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Threat of Zeon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will be returning to Zeon for a while{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...before I return, I promise you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want our people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I earned my promotion by being your son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well then, I look forward{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand how you feel. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...given your position as Sovereign...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...I beg you to carry out your duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabi! Zabi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabi! Zabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabi! Zabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabi! Zabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabi! Zabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabi! Zabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabi! Zabi! Zabi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this "interesting" thing you found?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! We've caught a warship that's not\Non our identification charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe it may be that Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be a chance\Nto avenge Lord Garma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so hasty, Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Their position is quite a distance\Nfrom our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to factor in our cruising range.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zanzibar can certainly make it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...the rest of our force is only made up of\Natmospheric entry capsules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, are you going to simply let them go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission is to avenge Garma's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to ignore\Ndirect orders from Admiral Dozle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're in the middle of atmospheric\Nentry. Please don't take unnecessary risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you hate the kind of man\Nwho would let someone pass by...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...without lifting a finger to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Repairs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, feeling down. Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is that?\N- The Gundam's spare computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, eat before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, brainwave levels low.\NLevels...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Haro, don't disturb him. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later. I'll come pick up your tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The main engine's third nozzle\Nhas 2% less thrust than displayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is that, in concrete terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,About 40 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we leave it until it got this bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't had time\Nfor proper maintenance, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a playground! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're... not playing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the third nozzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a break, Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please continue cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be the responsible one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, everyone relies on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a hard time believing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Zeon. It looks likeule...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but It seems too big for that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What has been done about Char?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably went back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Dozle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my lady. Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Block number 6 is hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can't we shake them off?\N- Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're using speed from the entry,\Nand our engines are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head into those clouds, starboard side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be going into a thunder storm.\NAre you sure...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The beam cannon's power\Nwill be halved, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a new Zeon weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. No matter what new weapon\Nattacks, the Gundam will protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant!\NThe Federation's got a new weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic!\NThis is what's known on Earth as lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before, on Earth.\NIt's all right, Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it does look frightening\Nup close like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But now that we know\Nthis is what they call lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us continue pursuing the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Port-side main engine losing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That earlier hit is affecting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good... especially at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the E.C. M?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's transmitting at maximum output.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai. We're going to have to land\Nsomewhere and wait this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're just\Nwasting Minovsky particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you do it?\N- I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward infrared observation monitor open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin laser sensor terrain scan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirm direction and approach angle!\NCan you do it, Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base is at zero speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Well done, Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam! Guncannon! Guntank!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for sortie! Open anti-aircraft fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to believe it, but are you still...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together! We have a sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoning out in your room\Nwon't do any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Get up! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. You don't have to hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse has completely vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They've slipped out of the laser search net.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't have escaped from this storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep searching for as long as\Nwe can stay in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!\NReleasing 180 degree infrared camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No response on sonar sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- There are a lot of islands in this area.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could use the radar,\Nwe'd find them right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't. I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're sure?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure he's up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This helmet feels strange.\NIt's suffocating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep going past us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's no mistake?\N- Yes. The magnetic response is too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out an FW flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Ramba Ral,lare.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the rear, at 7 o'clock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure it's not lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Hard turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Open main cannons!\NGundam, Guncannon! Prepare for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire even if you can't see anything!\NLaunch missiles, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's the famous Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get all the data you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than watching you sit around\Nlike a commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...I much prefer seeing you like this,\Ngoing into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.\NI think this suits me better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- See you. Don't let the soldiers interfere.\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Acous! Cozun! Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Yes, Lieutenant!s OK!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Acous, Cozun, this is our first time\Nfighting on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the enemy mobile suit appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't pursue it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamon, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fret, Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we cannot remain airborne\Nat this place any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your assistance.\NGo ahead to base. We'll follow soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger. We wish you success.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean, Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Komusais are leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably low on fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a better chance at winning now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam, Guncannon,\Nwhy aren't you launching?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zakus are on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, to tell the truth,yndrome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Make Amuro sortie as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing that will stop the Zakus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sink or swim, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! We have a sortie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Let's go! We're launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! We're about to launch! Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, do you read?ion Is complete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are launching.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yeah, Ms. Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't hear you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm launching, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, Sayla!\NJust launch the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it together, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a Zaku? No, it can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Z-Zaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's a new mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A new Zeon mobile suit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! Kai! Give Amuro some backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,White Base turrets, give him fire cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop all fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Acous! Throw the cracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is something.\NBut can it withstand the heat rod?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That mobile suit's pilot is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised he wasn't blown apart\Nby his own bazooka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lieutenant Ral, on your right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's another one coming out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's a mobile suit too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him covering fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Acous, Cozun, you handle\Nthe two mobile suits in back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go after the white one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you! I'll finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're a new mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Don't get too close to him!\NHis weapon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no Zaku, my friend! No Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's different!\NIt's got more armor and power than a Zaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Acous, Cozun, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- We're heading back!\N- Roger, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on board! Engage lock, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Message to the bridge.\NPrepare the blinding flood lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, they spared us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have lost a hero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But does this mean our defeat?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! It Is a new beginning!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zeon's national strength Is less thani\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In spite of that, how Is It thatong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My people!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It Is because the Principality of Zeon's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The damn Zeons are broadcasting this live\Nall over the world, just to annoy us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should watch too, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has been over fifty years\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...took control of the Earth Federation,\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We, who live In space,\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remember how many times the Federation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Principality of Zeon is fighting{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and God will not turn his back on us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My younger brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the Garma Zabi is dead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was a spoiled kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fighting has died down somewhat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps many of you see this war{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bartender!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- But that is a mistake! The Federation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...has polluted the Earth out of greed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...has polluted the Earth out of greed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- We must expose the foolishness...lia's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...of the Earth Federation elites...mander.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Garma died in order to wake you\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- This is only the beginning of our war.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- We are building up our military..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- The Earth Federation will do the same.{\i0}
