Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...died due to the Federation's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We must never forget!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Garma has shown us thisi\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By focusing our collective anger{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and bringing it down upon the Federation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Victory is the greatest tributee fallen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rise, my people!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take your sorrow and turn it into anger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zeon thirsts for your strength!{\i0}
