Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's childhood home is a place\Nwhere ally and enemy tangle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...and people live with despairing hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As the son encounters his mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...misfortune threatens them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing his mother again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...does not bring Amuro peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, on Mobile Suit Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming Home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
